cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.MS, cs.SY, cs.OH. 

This paper focuses on software engineering practices to improve the energy efficiency of mobile apps. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of automatic refactoring, which falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages). The analysis of code smells and the use of a tool to detect them can be categorized under cs.MS (Measurement and Analysis). The energy efficiency aspect of the paper can also be related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.OH (Other Computer Science).
